import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; export default function App() { const [businessData, setBusinessData] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { axios .get("http://localhost:3001/api/data") .then((response) => setBusinessData(response.data)) .catch((error) => console.error("Error fetching data:", error)); }, []); return (
{businessData.map((business) => ( ))}
business_id name address city state postal_code stars review_count is_open categories
{business.business_id} {business.name} {business.address} {business.city} {business.state} {business.postal_code} {business.stars} {business.review_count} {business.is_open} {business.categories}
); }
